    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>修仙主题的背包管理+肉鸽爬塔游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【背包管理】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过法宝、功法、材料、防具、策令等各具特色的道具，自由组合你的构建套路，每一把都是不一样的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067850/extras/7ba87deb4b729dca84d56da1bff417c7.poster.avif?t=1744143008\" width=604 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067850/extras/7ba87deb4b729dca84d56da1bff417c7.webm?t=1744143008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067850/extras/7ba87deb4b729dca84d56da1bff417c7.mp4?t=1744143008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【爬塔肉鸽】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一层层爬塔历练，四个各具特色的大场景，挑战数十位独特技能和行为方式的首领。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067850/extras/b23680683b634631bd04ffedaa0c5b09.poster.avif?t=1744143008\" width=594 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067850/extras/b23680683b634631bd04ffedaa0c5b09.webm?t=1744143008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067850/extras/b23680683b634631bd04ffedaa0c5b09.mp4?t=1744143008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067850/extras/19340f8fcc156d75100edfadbbe0175f.poster.avif?t=1744143008\" width=604 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067850/extras/19340f8fcc156d75100edfadbbe0175f.webm?t=1744143008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3067850/extras/19340f8fcc156d75100edfadbbe0175f.mp4?t=1744143008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【世界探索】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了关卡战斗外，大世界是一个可供探索的区域，包含隐藏场景【鬼市】和【白玉京】可供探索寻宝。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
